

/src - This directory should contain only application source files.


Coding style

	Read https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0008/ before you write your first line of code, please.


Comments

	Make brief and usable comments in each file. Use doxygen comment style as is mentioned at
	https://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen/manual/docblocks.html#pythonblocks

	Each file should contain following header:

		##
		# @file file_name.py
		# @author John Doe <john.doe@stud.fit.vutbr.cz>
		# @date 2016-04-08
		# @brief Short description of file.
		#
		# Long description of file.
		##
		